			<a href="https://bouqs.com/blog/early-spring-flowers/" ><img width="1080" height="719" src="https://bouqs.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/shutterstock_260182148-min-1080x719.jpg" class="attachment-full-thumb size-full-thumb wp-post-image" alt="Field of colorful tulips on a bright sunny day." srcset="https://bouqs.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/shutterstock_260182148-min-1080x719.jpg 1080w, https://bouqs.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/shutterstock_260182148-min-400x266.jpg 400w, https://bouqs.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/shutterstock_260182148-min-768x511.jpg 768w, https://bouqs.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/shutterstock_260182148-min-826x550.jpg 826w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px" /></a>
